### Sign in as an existing patient
POST http://localhost:3000/patients/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test1@test.com",
    "password": "123test",
    "type": "patient"
}

### Get the currently signed in patient
GET http://localhost:3000/patients/currentUser


